{"version":3,"kind":"Article","sha256":"0d9d363c316155a56b50c66122b0d5223b69647d0feb3c8415d40872ead6612d","slug":"index-37","location":"/profile/product/qtcloud_think/index.md","dependencies":[],"frontmatter":{"title":"思考云","content_includes_title":false,"github":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech","keywords":["quanttide","documentation"],"numbering":{"title":{"offset":3}},"source_url":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech/blob/main/docs/profile/product/qtcloud_think/index.md","edit_url":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech/edit/main/docs/profile/product/qtcloud_think/index.md","exports":[{"format":"md","filename":"index.md","url":"/index-a045b271f43cd323207742c841d51bb7.md"}]},"mdast":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"block","children":[{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"收集","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"key":"NeQWIi5VI0"}],"identifier":"id","label":"收集","html_id":"id","implicit":true,"key":"VWK6262E5I"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":1},"end":{"line":5,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"提取","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":1},"end":{"line":5,"column":1}},"key":"Jo3xW5mOUT"}],"key":"vUy8ioJaeA"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1},"end":{"line":7,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在复杂交互中，通过分层、提炼和结构化，让信息既能深度处理，又能灵活暂停与恢复。","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1},"end":{"line":7,"column":1}},"key":"Ui3BVInzzR"}],"key":"u6N5zSvAGA"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1},"end":{"line":9,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"组织","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1},"end":{"line":9,"column":1}},"key":"tviVviUQvo"}],"key":"GPHCTsYVdZ"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1},"end":{"line":15,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"问题\t表现\n透明度不足\t用户看不到总结是如何生成的\n速度问题\t澄清过程拖沓，打断心流\n输出质量\t总结结果不够理想\n退出机制\t缺乏优雅的”暂停-续作“设计","position":{"start":{"line":11,"column":1},"end":{"line":11,"column":1}},"key":"KyvaO1Ewvl"}],"key":"xGcBwBDYIC"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":1},"end":{"line":18,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"核心矛盾：暂停 vs 遗忘\n你的直觉是对的：Message 全存，Note 遗忘","position":{"start":{"line":17,"column":1},"end":{"line":17,"column":1}},"key":"oLIC3wSohJ"}],"key":"StCsGyrjUZ"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":20,"column":1},"end":{"line":21,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Q: 用户暂停后，Message 层要不要给 AI 看？\n建议：摘要化呈现，而非原始对话","position":{"start":{"line":20,"column":1},"end":{"line":20,"column":1}},"key":"yYbzd4AV4m"}],"key":"iwNbhQgd7Q"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":23,"column":1},"end":{"line":27,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"如果现在只改一点：\n在暂停时强制生成”已确认清单“和”待探索清单“\n这比完整的总结更快（解决速度问题），\n结构比段落更清晰（解决透明度问题），\n同时为未来恢复提供锚点（解决遗忘问题）。","position":{"start":{"line":23,"column":1},"end":{"line":23,"column":1}},"key":"RmGIjVkwIu"}],"key":"DzgOjAjBVI"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":29,"column":1},"end":{"line":32,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"你提到目前“总结过程不够透明，速度偏慢，结果不够理想”。这通常是由于缺乏中间状态的提炼。\n●     引入“中间节点”：\n●     不要等到最后一步才总结。\n●     在每一轮澄清结束时，生成一个极简的中间摘要（例如： [澄清点] -> [结论] ）。","position":{"start":{"line":29,"column":1},"end":{"line":29,"column":1}},"key":"m0FgH6gpqe"}],"key":"ewzpv894Nz"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":35,"column":1},"end":{"line":35,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"收集","position":{"start":{"line":35,"column":1},"end":{"line":35,"column":1}},"key":"pEmoOSd1e6"}],"key":"GVBLmeFtU6"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":37,"column":1},"end":{"line":37,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"目前已经是一个完整的最小循环。会澄清，允许用户选择退出。总结过程不够透明，速度偏慢，总结结果不够理想。是否允许用户在轮次过多时停下来，之后有时间精力再继续深入。但是这样又会可能过一阵子就忘记了。遗忘机制如何设计和如何发生，可能会有什么副作用，怎么避免。是不是要考虑把 Message 和 Note 都记录下来，遗忘主要发生在 Note 层。是想让 Note 可以过期。","position":{"start":{"line":37,"column":1},"end":{"line":37,"column":1}},"key":"KeBteG290y"}],"key":"puddWqA8Ho"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":39,"column":1},"end":{"line":39,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"这个容器得能容纳关于迭代自己的想法，不然怎么迭代别人。","position":{"start":{"line":39,"column":1},"end":{"line":39,"column":1}},"key":"DnB0yxDkjm"}],"key":"cny1UUjQv2"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":41,"column":1},"end":{"line":41,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"设置 meta这样我可以和 meta 互相观察，左脚踩右脚迭代","position":{"start":{"line":41,"column":1},"end":{"line":41,"column":1}},"key":"YhiCfFKHTh"}],"key":"zWm9nXEKll"}],"key":"J5CY9gzOE9"}],"key":"g0H1q557fF"},"references":{"cite":{"order":[],"data":{}}}}